obj_root_law_sections_1:
  sectionId (39000)
  sectionNo (1)
  orderNo 1
  title `Title, extent and saving.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_1_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517&sectionId=39000&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517
obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line `(1) This Act may be called the Partition Act, 1893.`
  line
  line `(2) It extends to the whole of India ^1*** ^2***.`
  line
  line ^3*****
  line
  line `(4) But nothing herein contained shall be deemed to affect any local law providing for the partition of immoveable property paying revenue to Government.`
obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. The words "except the State of Jammu and Kashmir" omitted by Act 34 of 2019, s. 95 and the Fifth Schedule`
  line `(w.e.f. 31-10-2019)..`
  line
  line `2. The word "and" rep. by Act 10 of 1914, s. 3 and the Second Schedule.`
  line
  line `3. Sub-section (3) rep. by s. 3 and the Second Schedule, ibid.`
obj_root_law_sections_2:
  sectionId (39001)
  sectionNo (2)
  orderNo 2
  title `Power to court to order sale instead of division in partition suits.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_2_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517&sectionId=39001&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517
obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line `Whenever in any suit for`
  line `partition in which, if instituted prior to the commencement of this Act, a decree for partition might have`
  line `been made, it appears to the court that, by reason of the nature of the properly to which the suit relates, or`
  line `of the number of the shareholders therein, or of any other special circumstance, a division of the property`
  line `cannot reasonably or conveniently be made, and that a sale of the property and distribution of the`
  line `proceeds would be more beneficial for all the shareholders, the court may, if it thinks fit, on the request of`
  line `any of such shareholders interested individually or collectively to the extent of one moiety or upwards,`
  line `direct a sale of the property and a distribution of the proceeds.`
obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_3:
  sectionId (39002)
  sectionNo (3)
  orderNo 3
  title `Procedure when sharer undertakes to buy.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_3_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517&sectionId=39002&sectionno=3&orderno=3&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517
obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line `(1) If, in any case in which the court is requested`
  line `under the last foregoing section to direct a sale, any other shareholder applies for leave to buy at a`
  line `valuation the share or shares of the party or parties asking for a sale, the court shall order a valuation of`
  line `the share or shares in such manner as it may think fit and offer to sell the same to such shareholder at the`
  line `price so ascertained, and may give all necessary and proper directions in that behalf.`
  line
  line `(2) If two or more shareholders severally apply for leave to buy as provided in sub-section (1), the`
  line `court shall order a sale of the share or shares to the shareholder who offers to pay the highest price above`
  line `the valuation made by the court.`
  line
  line `(3) If no such shareholder is willing to buy such share or shares at the price so ascertained, the`
  line `applicant or applicants shall be liable to pay all costs of or incident to the application or applications.`
obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_4:
  sectionId (39003)
  sectionNo (4)
  orderNo 4
  title `Partition suit by transferee of share in dwelling-house.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_4_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517&sectionId=39003&sectionno=4&orderno=4&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517
obj_root_law_sections_4_content:
  string
  line `(1) Where a share of a dwelling-house`
  line `belonging to an undivided family has been transferred to a person who is not a member of such family`
  line `and such transferee sues for partition, the court shall, if any member of the family being a shareholder`
  line `shall undertake to buy the share of such transferee, make a valuation of such share in such manner as it`
  line `thinks fit and direct the sale of such share to such shareholder, and may give all necessary and proper`
  line `directions in that behalf.`
  line
  line `(2) If in any case described in sub-section (1) two or more members of the family being such`
  line `shareholders severally undertake to buy such share, the court shall follow the procedure prescribed by`
  line `sub-section (2) of the last foregoing section.`
obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_5:
  sectionId (39004)
  sectionNo (5)
  orderNo 5
  title `Representation of parties under disability.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_5_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517&sectionId=39004&sectionno=5&orderno=5&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517
obj_root_law_sections_5_content:
  string
  line `In any suit for partition a request for sale may be`
  line `made or an undertaking, or application for leave, to buy may be given or made on behalf of any party`
  line `under disability by any person authorised to act on behalf of such party in such suit, but the court shall not`
  line `be bound to comply with any such request, undertaking or application unless it is of opinion that the sale`
  line `or purchase will be for the benefit of the party under such disability.`
obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_6:
  sectionId (39005)
  sectionNo (6)
  orderNo 6
  title `Reserved bidding and bidding by shareholders.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_6_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_6_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517&sectionId=39005&sectionno=6&orderno=6&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517
obj_root_law_sections_6_content:
  string
  line `(1) Every sale under section 2 shall be subject`
  line `to a reserved bidding, and the amount of such bidding shall be fixed by the court in such manner as it may`
  line `think fit and may be varied from time to time.`
  line
  line `(2) On any such sale any of the shareholders shall be at liberty to bid at the sale on such terms as to`
  line `non-payment of deposit or as to setting off or accounting for the purchase-money or any part thereof`
  line `instead of paying the same as to the court may seem reasonable.`
  line
  line `(3) If two or more persons, of whom one is a shareholder in the property, respectively advance the`
  line `same sum at any bidding at such sale, such bidding shall be deemed to be the bidding of the shareholder.`
obj_root_law_sections_6_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_7:
  sectionId (39006)
  sectionNo (7)
  orderNo 7
  title `Procedure to be followed in case of sales.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_7_content
  footnotes `1 The words "or of the Court of the Recorder of Rangoon" omitted by the A.O. 1937.`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517&sectionId=39006&sectionno=7&orderno=7&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517
obj_root_law_sections_7_content:
  string
  line `Save as hereinbefore provided, when any property is`
  line `directed to be sold under this Act, the following procedure shall, as far as practicable, be adopted,`
  line `namely:--`
  line
  line `(a) if the property be sold under a decree or order of the High Court of Calcutta, Madras or`
  line `Bombay, in the exercise of its original jurisdiction, ^1*** the procedure of such court in its original`
  line `civil jurisdiction for the sale of property by the Registrar;`
  line
  line `(b) if the property be sold under a decree or order of any other court, such procedure as the High`
  line `Court may from time to time by rules prescribe in this behalf, and until such rules-art made the`
  line `procedure prescribed in the Code of Civil Procedure in respect of sales in execution of decrees.`
obj_root_law_sections_8:
  sectionId (39007)
  sectionNo (8)
  orderNo 8
  title `Orders for sale to be deemed decrees.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_8_content
  footnotes `1 . See now the Code of Civil Procedure, 1908 (Act 5 of 1908).`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517&sectionId=39007&sectionno=8&orderno=8&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517
obj_root_law_sections_8_content:
  string
  line `Any order for sale made by the court under section 2, 3`
  line `or 4 shall be deemed to be a decree within the meaning of section 2 of the ^1Code of Civil Procedure (14 of`
  line `1882).`
obj_root_law_sections_9:
  sectionId (39008)
  sectionNo (9)
  orderNo 9
  title `Saving of power to order partly partition and partly sale.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_9_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_9_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517&sectionId=39008&sectionno=9&orderno=9&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517
obj_root_law_sections_9_content:
  string
  line `In any suit for partition the court`
  line `may, if it shall think fit, make a decree for a partition of part of the property to which the suit relates and a`
  line `sale of the remainder under this Act`
obj_root_law_sections_9_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_10:
  sectionId (39009)
  sectionNo (10)
  orderNo 10
  title `Application of Act to pending suits.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_10_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_10_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517&sectionId=39009&sectionno=10&orderno=10&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00070_189304_1547448130517
obj_root_law_sections_10_content:
  string
  line `This Act shall apply to suits instituted before the`
  line `commencement thereof, in which no scheme for the partition of the partition has been finally approved by`
  line `the court`
obj_root_law_sections_10_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_translations:
  hi obj_root_law_translations_hi
obj_root_law_translations_hi:
  title `विभाजन अधिनियम, 1893`
